notes.body: Hello Kunal,     Greetings from PharmEasy!     Thank you for showing an interest in working as a partner with us.     Please click on the link below and fill in the requisite details:  https://pharmeasy.in/franchisestores     Kindly note that once the form is filled request you to kindly wait for 5 business days for the call, as there are certain conditions that our team will need to check before they connect with you to discuss your interest further.     If you do not receive a call or email to take this further, it means that your partner's request has not been considered.     Also, please direct your query to our franchise team. Our franchise team will then contact you in case of any suitable prospects.  ​   For any further assistance, please reach out to us through our support channels in the App or website listed in the 'Need Help' section.     Thank you for choosing PharmEasy. Stay Healthy.     Regards,  Manisha
notes.body_html:
Hello Kunal,

Greetings from PharmEasy!
 
Thank you for showing an interest in working as a partner with us.
 
Please click on the link below and fill in the requisite details:
https://pharmeasy.in/franchisestores
 
Kindly note that once the form is filled request you to kindly wait for 5 business days for the call, as there are certain conditions that our team will need to check before they connect with you to discuss your interest further.

If you do not receive a call or email to take this further, it means that your partner's request has not been considered.

Also, please direct your query to our franchise team. Their email ID is franchisequery@pharmeasy.in, and they can assist you better. Kindly provide them with complete details and a valid contact number so that they can connect with you. Our franchise team will then contact you in case of any suitable prospects.
​
For any further assistance, please reach out to us through our support channels in the App or website listed in the 'Need Help' section.

Thank you for choosing PharmEasy. Stay Healthy.

Regards,
Manisha

Hello Zaid,

Greetings from PharmEasy! 
 
Thank you for showing an interest in working as a Franchisee partner with us.

If you do not receive a call or email to take this further, it means that your partner's request has not been considered.

For any further assistance, please reach out to us through our support channels, in the App or website, listed in the 'Need Help' section.

Thank you for choosing PharmEasy. Stay healthy!

Regards,
Habiba
